subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: Frank Lickliter II shot a four-under 68 at Orange County National to take a five-stroke lead after the fifth of six rounds at the PGA Tour National Qualifying Tournament in Winter Garden, Fla. The top 25 finishers and ties in the 166-man field will earn 2008 PGA Tour cards.
